description: This file contains utility functions for the game logic of a Tic Tac Toe game, including functions to check the winner and to get the AI's move.

methods.name: checkWinner
methods.description: Checks the current state of the Tic Tac Toe board to determine if there is a winner or if the game is a draw.

methods.name: getAIMove
methods.description: Calculates the AI's next move by finding the first empty cell on the Tic Tac Toe board.

ctags.name: getAIMove
ctags.pattern: /^export const getAIMove = (board: string[][]): { row: number; col: number } => {$/
